title: Ep 148: Career and Love
description: This episode I took a trip to NY and it got me thinking all kinds of thoughts on this simulation known as reality. How do we find the career we want? How do we pursue the love we want? I answer some emails about this and get super deep, bros!
author: nadav@ymhstudios.com (Christina Pazsitzky)
